NAME

       Sjis - Source code filter for ShiftJIS script

SYNOPSIS

    In your script:

      use Sjis;

    At command prompt:

      without "use Sjis;" in your script
        jperl55.bat   yourscript.pl  param1  param2 ...
        jperl58.bat   yourscript.pl  param1  param2 ...
        jperl510.bat  yourscript.pl  param1  param2 ...

      with "use Sjis;" in your script
        perl.exe     yourscript.pl  param1  param2 ...
        perl58.bat   yourscript.pl  param1  param2 ...
        perl510.bat  yourscript.pl  param1  param2 ...

DESCRIPTION

      This software is "JPerl" written by Perl.
      We can write the script in ShiftJIS again.

      This is software that does the bridge from JPerl to Perl of the
      latest version.

      This software is still an alpha version for expressing a concept.

INSTALLATION

To install this software, type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL    --- Makefile.PL makes "make.bat" only, and ...
   make.bat
   make.bat test
   perl t\smoke.pl
   perl t\shiftjis.htm\shiftjis.htm.pl

   make.bat install              --- install to current using Perl
   perl58.bat make.bat instal    --- install to Perl5.8
   perl510.bat make.bat install  --- install to Perl5.10

MAKE OTHER

   make.bat dist       --- make distribution package
   make.bat tar.bat    --- make perl script "tar.bat"

PROGRAM COMPOSITION

    Sjis.pm      --- source code filter for ShiftJIS script
    esjis.pl     --- source code filter to escape ShiftJIS
    Esjis.pm     --- run-time routines for esjis.pl
    jperl55.bat  --- jperl emulator by perl5.5  with esjis.pl
    jperl58.bat  --- jperl emulator by perl5.8  with esjis.pl
    jperl510.bat --- jperl emulator by perl5.10 with esjis.pl
    perl58.bat   --- find and run perl5.8  without %PATH% settings
    perl510.bat  --- find and run perl5.10 without %PATH% settings
    pl2ebat      --- escape and wrap ShiftJIS perl code into a batch file

DEPENDENCIES

This software requires perl5.00503 or later and perl5.008 or perl5.010.

